Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧让周围的人进行增援
